---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="border-t border-white/5 px-6 py-10">
	<div class="mx-auto flex max-w-6xl flex-col items-center justify-between gap-4 sm:flex-row">
		<p class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-bold text-white">
			<span class="text-emerald-400">&lt;/&gt;</span>
			repo<span class="text-fuchsia-400">.lat</span>
		</p>
		<p class="text-sm text-slate-500">
			Hecho con 💚 por la comunidad LATAM · {year}
		</p>
		<a
			href="https://github.com/LlamaTrix/repo.lat"
			class="text-sm text-slate-400 transition hover:text-white"
		>
			Código en GitHub →
		</a>
	</div>
</footer>
